    id: 'parental-guardian-rights',
    title: 'VII. Parental/Guardian Rights',
    body: `
<p>Parents or guardians can review or have their child's personal information deleted and may refuse further collection or use. To exercise these rights, email <a href="mailto:info@jointheleague.org">info@jointheleague.org</a> or mail your request to The LEAGUE of Amazing Programmers, 12625 High Bluff Drive #107, San Diego, CA 92130. You can also call (858) 284-0481.</p>
`,
