<p>Forums and chat rooms may be available. Content posted there can be read by anyone. Information shared in these areas could include personal details visible to others and is no longer private. We cannot guarantee the security of information disclosed in public areas, and users participate at their own risk. We reserve the right to monitor content and remove age-inappropriate or personally identifiable information.</p>
`,
