  {
    id: 'links-and-third-parties',
    title: 'X. Links and Third Parties',
    body: `
<p>We may include or offer third-party websites, products, and services on LEAGUE Sites &amp; Services. These third parties maintain independent privacy policies, and we are not responsible for their content or activities. Our sites may also contain links to other resources provided for convenience. These external sites are not under our control, and accessing them is at your own risk.</p>
`,
  },
  {
    id: 'international-visitors',
    title: 'XI. International Visitors',
    body: `
<p>LEAGUE Sites &amp; Services are operated on servers located in the United States. By using LEAGUE Sites &amp; Services from the European Union or other regions with different data laws, you consent to transferring your personal information to the United States.</p>
`,
  },
  {
    id: 'data-security',
    title: 'XII. Data Security Commitment',
    body: `
<p>We implement reasonable physical, electronic, and managerial procedures to safeguard information. Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) protocol protects sensitive personal information on account and registration pages. Sensitive data is encrypted on LEAGUE Sites &amp; Services and when stored on servers.</p>
`,
  },
  {
    id: 'access-correct-delete',
    title: 'XIII. How You Can Access, Request a Copy, Correct, or Ask for Information to Be Deleted',
    body: `
<p>Certain personal information collected through our services may be available to you. If you created a password-protected account, you can access it to review the information provided.</p>
<p>You may also email or mail us to request a copy, correction, or deletion of personal information. Include registration details such as name, phone, and email address. We may request additional information to verify identity.</p>
<p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@jointheleague.org">info@jointheleague.org</a><br />
Phone: 1-858-284-0481</p>
`,
  },
  {
    id: 'contact-and-opt-out',
    title: 'XIV. How to Contact Us / Opting Out of Electronic Communications',
    body: `
<p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, or if you have provided your email or address and prefer not to receive marketing information, contact us via email or phone. Provide your name and the email addresses or mailing addresses to remove.</p>
<p>If you signed up for text messages and wish to stop receiving them, call or email us with your name, account email, and phone number(s) to remove.</p>
<p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@jointheleague.org">info@jointheleague.org</a><br />
Phone: 1-858-284-0481</p>
`,
